\begin{abstract}
In the present paper, we study pointwise pseudo-slant submanifold of a para-Kaehler manifold $\widetilde{M}^{2n}$. The conditions of integrability and totally geodesic foliation for the  distributions involved with the definition of a pointwise pseudo-slant submanifold are obtained. A necessary and sufficient condition for pointwise pseudo-slant submanfold $M$ to be locally warped product is derived in terms of Weingarten operator. We also, presented an example illustrating pointwise pseudo-slant warped product submanifold  of $\widetilde{M}^{2n}$.
\end{abstract}
